Another top contender on the list is the <strong>Mediterranean International Cup (MIC)</strong>, held annually in Spain's Costa Brava region. This prestigious tournament attracts youth teams from around the world, offering both boys' and girls' competitions across various age categories.

&nbsp;

The MIC is renowned for its high-level competition, with many professional clubs sending their youth teams to participate. Besides the intense soccer action, the tournament also features cultural and social events, making it a holistic experience for players, coaches, and families.

