For over 30 years, <strong>Copa Santa</strong> has been the go-to Easter tournament for more than 200 youth soccer teams worldwide. Held in the stunning regions of Costa Brava and Costa del Maresme, this event offers an authentic soccer festival experience, ideal for the entire family.

&nbsp;

Copa Santa provides a full immersion into international soccer, coupled with the charm of Spain during the spring holidays. It’s a must-visit for any youth soccer enthusiast looking for top-tier competition and cultural exploration.

